Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:40.99,English-IS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Tohle počasí mít rád se dá
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:45.00,Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}hikariga meni jasašikute
